game.name: Lords of the Realm II (1996) (Impressions).dosz
game.comment: Installed v1.03 from CD. Installation options: Full install Path: C:\LORDS2 (default) Sound: Sound Blaster 16, Port 220 Manually copied the FILES folder and MSSDRVR.LST from the disc, and copied SETSOUND.EXE into the main folder. SMK_HIGH files are moved into SMK_LOW instead. In LORDS2.INI, edit line 1 to: cdpath=C:\FILES The required LORDS2.INI is also in the DOSC.
game.comment_dosc: Required LORDS2.INI file, Sound Blaster 16 config, reduced game speed, and auto start

game.name: Metaltech - Earthsiege (1994) (Dynamix).dosz
game.comment: Installed v1.0 from CD, with some files manually copied, and patch applied. Also works with the freeware ISO released in 2015. Installation options: Directory: C:\SIERRA\MTECH (default) Installation Size: Full Digital Sound Driver: Sound Blaster 16, DMA 1, IRQ 7, Port 220h MIDI Music Driver: Use Digital Sound Card, Port 388h Manually copy PLAYFLIC.EXE and the FLIC folder from the CD. Then patch to v1.01. Follow the instructions and enter P D at the end. After, open ES.BAT and edit line 3 to: set ALT_DRIVE=c: Then open RESOURCE.CFG and edit line 21 to: pathFlic=.\flic\ And delete the empty line 19. The required ES.BAT and RESOURCE.CFG files are also in the DOSC.
game.comment_dosc: Required ES.BAT and RESOURCE.CFG files, and auto start. General MIDI option
